 Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/korpz/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

To add new plugins as submodules, add them to array in update_bundles.rb
